#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today‚Äôs topic is about helping your child learn and grow.\n"
"\n"
"Play helps children learn what is expected and how to get along with others. It supports their development, both in school and at home.\n"
"\n"
"This is true for all children, including those who are shy, have a disability, or struggle to keep up in class."
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje singokuncedisa umntwana wakho afunde kwaye akhule.\n"
"\n"
"Ukudlala kunceda abantwana bafunde oko kulindelekileyo nendlela yohlalisana nabanye. Ixhasa indlela abakhula ngayo, esikolweni nasekhaya.\n"
"\n"
"Oku kuyinyani kumntana wonke, ukuquka nabo banentloni, nabakhubazekileyo okanye kunzima ukuqhubeka ne klasi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Did you know that playing is the best way to relax AND learn? Tap play to learn more"
msgstr "Ubusazi ukuba ukudlala yeyona ndlela yokuphumla kwaye ufunde? Cofa Dlala ukuze ufunde ngakumbi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone!\n"
"Do you know what is the best way to relax? Playing! \n"
"\n"
"And let‚Äôs be honest, which child does not like to play? \n"
"\n"
"Learning takes time, but there is a lot that you can do as a parent to help your child. Let them play and explore. Let them ask questions and learn from mistakes. And be patient. Your support will help them grow and develop."
msgstr ""
"Molweni nonke!\n"
"\n"
"Uyayazi ukuba yeyiphi eyona ndlela yokuphumla? Ukudlala!\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye masinyaniseke, ngomphi umntwana ongathandi ukudlala?\n"
"\n"
"Ukufunda kuthatha ixeshaUkufunda kuthatha ixesha, kodwa kuninzi onkukwenza njengomzali ukunceda umntwana wakho. Bayeke badlale kwaye baphonononge. Bayeke babue imibuzo kwaye bafunde kwimpazamo. Kwaye ubenomonde, Inkxaso yakho iyakubanceda bakhule kwaye baphuhlise."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f3_mother.name knows that children learn best by playing. \n"
"She wants to help her son, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, grow and stay curious by spending more time playing together. Let‚Äôs see how she does it."
msgstr "U@data.characters.f3_mother.name uyayazi ukuba abantwana bafunda kakuhle ngokudlala. Ufuna ukunceda unyana wakhe, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, akhule kwaye ahlale enomdla ngokuchitha ixesha elininzi bedlala kunye. Masibone ukuba wenza njani."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hi @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, would you like to do something fun together?"
msgstr "Molo @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, ungathanda ukuba senze into eyonwabisayo kunye?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ooooh yes!"
msgstr "Ooooh ewe!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What would you like to do?"
msgstr "Ungathanda ukwenza ntoni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Build a house out of bed sheets!"
msgstr "Yakha indlu ngengubo yokulala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great idea! What do we need to do first?"
msgstr "Yingcinga entle! Kudingeka ukuba senze ntoni kuqala?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "First, we hang one bed sheet from the top bunk bed. It‚Äôs our first wall! Then, maybe we can use a pillow at the bottom."
msgstr "Kuqala, sixhoma ingubo ibenye kwinqanaba eliphezulu lwebhedi. Ludonga lwethu lokuqala! Emva koko, mhlawumbi singasebenzisa umqamelo ezantsi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It's lovely to see you thinking everything through so carefully."
msgstr "Kuyavuyisa ukubona ucinga yonke into ngocoselelo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! This is a wonderful bedsheet house."
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! Le yindlu entle yengubo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can we read our bedtime story here tonight?"
msgstr "Singalifundela apha ibali lethu lokulala ebusuku?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f3_mother.name helped her son learn by playing together. Let‚Äôs explore how she did this."
msgstr "U@data.characters.f3_mother.name uncedise unyana wakhe afunde ukuba badlale kunye. Masijonge ukuba uyenze njani lento."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f3_mother.name helped her son learn new skills by:\n"
"- ‚öΩ **Playing with him**: This let @data.characters.f3_son_4.name learn through doing. @data.characters.f3_mother.name didn‚Äôt need to show him how to build a house, he figured it out on his own.\n"
"- üèÜ **Letting him lead**: She allowed him to ask questions and explore. Curiosity helps children become confident and creative.\n"
"- üëèüèæ **Praising him**: She showed him that being curious and trying ideas is a good thing."
msgstr ""
"U@data.characters.f3_mother.name uncedise unyana wakhe ukuba afunde isakhona esitsha ngokuthi:\n"
"- ‚öΩ **Edlal naye**: Lento yenze u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name afunde ngokwenza. U@data.characters.f3_mother.name khange adinge ukumbonisa ukuba yakhiwa njani indlu, wazicingela ngokwakhe.\n"
"- üèÜ **Emyeka ekhokela**: Uye wamvumela abuze imibuzo kwaye afunde.Ukuthanda ukwazi kunceda abantwana bazithembe kwaye bayile.\n"
"- üëèüèæ **Ukumncoma**: Wambonisa ukuba ubenomdla kwaye nokuzama imibono yinto elungileyo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What did @data.characters.f3_son_4.name learn when his mother played with him?"
msgstr "Ufunde ntoni u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name xa umama wakhe ebedlala naye?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How to lead and give instructions"
msgstr "Indlela yokukhokela kunye nokunika imiyalelo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes! Actually, he learned all of these things! \n"
"\n"
"By leading the game, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name learned how to give clear instructions and be in charge. This is a very important skill for the future!"
msgstr ""
"Ewe! Kunjalo, uzifundile zonke ezi zinto!\n"
"\n"
"Ngokukhokela umdlalo u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name ufundile ukuba ukunika imiyalelo ecacileyo nokuba anagphatha.Esi sisakhono esibalulekileyo kakhulu kwixesha elizayo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How to be innovative"
msgstr "Indlela yokwazisa"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes! Actually, he learned all of these things! \n"
"\n"
"By using his imagination, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name finds a new way to use a bed sheet. In his mind, it could be a castle or a rocketship. Being creative helps children build important skills for the future."
msgstr ""
"Ewe! Enyanisweni wazifunda zonke ezizinto!\n"
"\n"
"Ngokusebenzisa intekelelo yakhe, u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name wafumanisa indlela entsha yokusebenzisa ingubo yebhedi. Engqondweni yakhe, ingayinqaba okanye inqwelomoya. Ubuchule bokuyila kunceda abantwana bakhe izakhono ezibalulekileyo kwikamva."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How to problem solves"
msgstr "Indlela yokusombulula ingxaki"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes! Actually, he learned all of these things! \n"
"\n"
"By imagining a new kind of tent and solving a problem, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name is building important skills for school and life."
msgstr ""
"Ewe! Eneneni wafund kwezizinto! \n"
"\n"
"Ngokuthekelela uhlobo olutsha lentente kwaye nokusombulula ingxaki, u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name wakha izakhono ezibalulekileyo esikolweni nasebomini."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes, when the accident happens, he first asks if @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name is okay! \n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Ewe,xa bekusenzeka ingozi,uqale wabuza uku ba @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name uyaphila!\n"
"Zonke ezindlela ziyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He thanks @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name for recognising her mistake"
msgstr "Ubulele @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name ngokuqonda impazamo yakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes, praise helps our children to take more responsibility for their actions next time. \n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Ewe, ukuncoma kunceda abantwana ukuthatha uxanduva ngakumbi ngezenzo zabo kwixesha elizayo.\n"
" Zonke ezindlela ziyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He asks @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name to reflect on her behaviour"
msgstr "Ucele u @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name ukuba azihlolisise ngendlela aziphethe ngayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes, he helps her learn by asking her how she could have prevented the mistake. \n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr "Ewe, Umncedise ukuba afunde ngokumbuza ukuba wayenokuyiphepha kanjani impazamo!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He involves @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name to resolve the situation together"
msgstr "Ubandakanye u @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name ukusombulula imeko kunye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes, by asking her to help clean up, he shows how she can make things right again after making a mistake. \n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Ewe, ngokumcela ancedise ekucoceni, ubonisa indlela anokulunga ngayo emva kokwenza impazamo.\n"
"zonke ezindlela ziyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_uncle.name‚Äôs
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What does @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name learn from @data.characters.f3_uncle.name‚Äôs response?"
msgstr "Ufundani u @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name kwimpendulo ka @data.characters.f3_uncle.name‚Äôs?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is okay to make mistakes"
msgstr "Kulungile ukwenza impazamo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am still loved even if I make mistakes"
msgstr "Ndisathandwa nangona ndisenza impazamo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I can learn from my mistakes"
msgstr "Ndingafunda kwimpazamo zam"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Apologising is important"
msgstr "Ukuxolisa kubalulekile"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I can help to make things right again"
msgstr "Ndinganceda ukwenza izinto zilunge kwakhona"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_uncle.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly! @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name learns important things because @data.characters.f3_uncle.name responds in a calm and supportive way."
msgstr "Nqo! @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name ufunde izinto ezibalulekileyo kuba u @data.characters.f3_uncle.name uphendula ngendlela ezolileyo nexhasayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some tips to help you support your child as they learn and develop important skills."
msgstr "Nazi ezinye ingcebiso zokunceda uxhase umntwana wakho njengoko efunda kwaye ephuhlisa izakhono ezibalulekileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "LEARN BY PLAYING"
msgstr "FUNDA NGOKUDLALA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Play helps children develop important physical and social skills. \n"
"\n"
"Set aside time to play games with your child, be creative, and have fun together. Remember, through play, you also learn what kind of support your child may need."
msgstr ""
"Ukudlala kunceda ukuphuhlisa izakhono ezibalulekileyo ngokwasemzimbeni nezentlalo.\n"
"\n"
"Beka ecaleni ixesha lokudlala imidlalo nomntana wakho, yiba nobuchule nonwabe kunye. Khumbula, ngokudlala uyafunda kanjalo uhlobo lwenxaso umntwana wakho aludingayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You can support your child to play and make friends with other children, so they learn how to interact with others well. \n"
"\n"
"If your child starts to feel overwhelmed with anything in their day, help them reduce their stress by taking a pause and playing together."
msgstr ""
"Ungaxhasa umntwana wakho ngokudlala futhi enze ubuhlobo nabanaye abantwana, ukuze bafunde ukuba kunxulumanwa kanjani nabanye kanjalo.\n"
"Ukuba umntwana wakho uqalisa ukuziva enganyelwe nangantonina kusuku lwakhe, bancedise ukwehlisa uxinzelelo ngokuphumla kancinci nidlale kunye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BE PATIENT"
msgstr "Yiba nomonde"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Learning new things takes time. Be patient and encourage your child to keep trying, even when things feel hard. \n"
"\n"
"Stay calm when they get angry or frustrated ‚Äì your child will learn to do the same over time."
msgstr ""
"Ukufunda izinto ezintsha kuthatha ixesha. Yiba nomonde kwaye ukhuthaze umntwana wakho ukuqhubeka ezama, noba izinto zivakala zinzima.\n"
"hlala unomoya ophantsi xa besiba nomsindo okanye bekhungathekile - Umntwaa wakho uyakufunda ukwenza okufanayo ngokuhamba kwexesha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You can support them by praising them for trying, and helping them break large tasks into smaller tasks that are appropriate for their age.\n"
"\n"
"Use play to help your child learn difficult skills, like losing, sharing, or taking turns."
msgstr "Ungabaxhasa ngokubanacoma kuba bezamile kwaye ukubanceda ukwahlula imisebenzi emikhulu ibe yimesebenzi emincinci efanelekileyo kwiminyaka yabo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SUPPORT CURIOSITY"
msgstr "XHASA IMINQWENO YABO YOKWAZI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Children learn by asking questions and exploring the things they are interested in. Give your child time and space to do this, and be patient when they make mistakes. We all learn from our mistakes!"
msgstr "Abantwana bafunda ngokubuza imibuzo kwaye baphande ngezinto abanomdla kuzo. Nika umntwana wakho ixesha nethuba ukwenza lento, kwaye ubenomonde xa besenza amaphutha. Sonke sifunda kumaphutha ethu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye ingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your child may talk a lot and have many questions ‚Äì  including difficult ones. You can give your child short but honest answers. \n"
"\n"
"If you need a break or more information, you can take a pause and tell your child you will respond to them later."
msgstr ""
"Umntwana wakho anagthetha kakhulu kwaye abenemibuzo emininzi - ekubandakanya eyona enzima. Unganika umntwana wakho impendulo emfutshane kodwa eyinyani.\n"
"Xa udinga ukhefu okanye ezinye incukacha ezithe vetshe, ungama kancinci kwaye uxelele umntwana wakho ukuba uzakuhendula ethubeni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now that you‚Äôve learned tips to support your child‚Äôs learning through play, let‚Äôs come up with some practical ideas to try out!"
msgstr "Njengoba ngoku ufundile ingcebiso ukuxhasa umntwana wakho ukufunda bedlala, masize nembono ezisebenza onokuzizama!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What could you do to encourage your child to play and learn?"
msgstr "Ungenza ntoni ukukhuthaza umntwana wakho ukudlala kwaye afunde?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Join their play"
msgstr "Zibandakanye emidlalweni yabo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That‚Äôs right! Join in on any play activity your child is doing. You will strengthen your bond and encourage your child to play and learn more."
msgstr "Kulungile! zibandakanye nakowuphi umdlalo umntwana wakho awenzayo. Uyakomeleza ubudlelwane benu kwaye ukhuthaze umntwana wakho ukudlala kwaye afunde ngakumbi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Go outside together"
msgstr "Iyani phandle kunye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great idea. Try to look for opportunities to play and learn, like collecting leaves or rocks on the way home from school."
msgstr "Umbono omhle. Zama ukujonga amathuba okudlala kwaye afunde, njengokuqokelela amagqabi okanye amatye endleleni esuka esikolweni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use household items"
msgstr "Sebenzisa izinto ezise ndlini"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes! Get creative. Anything in your home could be a musical instrument, costume, or item in a role-play."
msgstr "Ewe! Yiba nobuchule. nantoni na esendlini yakho ingasisixhobo somculo, i sinxibo somdlalo, izinto ezisetyenziswayo kumdlalo wokulinganisa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask their ideas"
msgstr "Cela imbono zabo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Other"
msgstr "Enye indlela"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

